net.sourceforge.gjtapi.raw.remote
Class CorbaListenerWrapper

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--net.sourceforge.gjtapi.raw.remote.CorbaListenerWrapper
public class CorbaListenerWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements TelephonyListener

This wraps a CorbaListener and makes it look like a TelephonyListener again. The TelephonyProvider can then deal with TelephonyListenerss as if they are local. Creation date: (2000-02-17 13:36:23)
